## Goal
- Complete overhaul of the "Gestion des Documents Véhicules" module + enrich vehicle history + transform Power BI for real data with multi-source fetching, auto-refresh, comprehensive filters, and AI

## Constraints & Preferences
- Replace all hardcoded `http://localhost:8080` URLs with relative proxy paths
- Use `Promise.all` with `.catch()` fallbacks
- Fetch block/unblock info from 5 data sources in priority order
- Iterate all blocage entries field-by-field (backend may not set `bloque` boolean)
- Use `fmtDate()` helper for string dates, array dates `[y,mo,d,h,mi]`, and null
- Use `as any` on axios `res.data` to fix TS18046 (unknown type)
- Match existing code patterns: `framer-motion` animations, recharts, lucide-react icons

