## Key Decisions
- Single `setVehicleHistory({...data, ...computed})` to flatten all enriched fields into one state object
- Source 1 (blocked-vehicules) checked first for current blocks; sources 2-5 fall back for unblocked vehicles
- Expired docs shown in separate "Re-créer" section above delay-based notification groups
- Write tool corrupted two files (index.tsx, ExecutiveDashboard.tsx) → restored via PowerShell Write tool
- All new API calls use relative `/api/...` paths (proxy handles routing to `localhost:8080`)
- `@WebMvcTest` used for controller tests (focused slice, fast), `@SpringBootTest` for integration (full context, H2)
- Test data seeder is a `@Component` for `@Autowired` injection into tests; uses `Random(42)` for reproducibility

